🧩 The Daily “Automatic Breathing” Protocol (15–25 min total)

🟢 1. Morning Reset (5 minutes)

Start your system correctly.
	•	10 slow nasal breaths
	•	4 sec in / 6 sec out
	•	Stand tall (posture stack)
	•	1 minute: breathe + hold posture

👉 This sets your baseline for the day

⸻

🟡 2. Movement Practice (walk/run)

Walking (daily):
	•	3 steps inhale / 3 steps exhale
	•	Nose only

Running (2–3x/week):
	•	2:2 breathing (steps)
	•	Stay relaxed, not intense

👉 This is where breathing becomes automatic

⸻

🔵 3. Speaking Training (this is the missing piece)

Most people never train this.

Do 5 minutes:
	•	Read something out loud
	•	Rules:
	•	inhale → speak
	•	pause instead of rushing
	•	slow down 20%

👉 This rewires:
	•	anxiety
	•	voice control
	•	confidence

⸻

🟣 4. Night Downshift (5–10 min)
	•	4–6 breathing
	•	or body scan

👉 This locks in recovery + sleep

⸻

🔁 The Real Game: “Catch & Correct”

This is where you actually change.

Throughout the day, notice:
	•	shallow breathing
	•	tight chest
	•	rushing speech

Then:

👉 Fix it immediately
	•	inhale through nose
	•	slow exhale
	•	relax shoulders

Even 10 seconds matters.

